---
title: Silky Sicilian Penne & Scallops tossed with Mushrooms, Zucchini & Tomatoes
description: If you’re mad for mushrooms or a fan of fungi, this pasta will treat you right: It’s loaded with ’shroom slices! They’re the flavor backbone of this recipe along with rich mushroom stock, bringing all those deep, earthy flavors that you know and love. We’ve added al dente penne, zucchini, tomatoes, a lemony, chive-flecked crème fraîche sauce, and a sprinkling of Parmesan cheese. Get ready for this umami-packed dish to hit your dinner table.
